  "title": "Construction Supervisor",
  "description": "<h2>Job Title: Construction Supervisor</h2><p><strong>Location:</strong> [Singapore]<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> [Full-time / Contract]<br /><strong>Experience Level:</strong> [Minimum 2 Years]</p><h3>Job Summary</h3><p>We are seeking an experienced and detail-oriented <strong>Construction Supervisor</strong> to oversee daily on-site operations and ensure construction projects are completed safely, on schedule, and within budget. The ideal candidate will coordinate workers, subcontractors, and materials while maintaining high standards of quality and compliance.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Supervise and coordinate daily construction activities on-site</p></li><li><p>Ensure projects follow approved plans, drawings, and specifications</p></li><li><p>Manage construction crews and subcontractors</p></li><li><p>Monitor project schedules and report progress to management</p></li><li><p>Enforce safety regulations and company policies at all times</p></li><li><p>Inspect work quality and resolve on-site issues promptly</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with engineers, architects, and suppliers</p></li><li><p>Maintain site records, reports, and attendance logs</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Construction Supervisor or similar role</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of construction methods, materials, and regulations</p></li><li><p>Ability to read and interpret drawings and technical documents</p></li><li><p>Excellent leadership and communication skills</p></li><li><p>Strong problem-solving and decision-making abilities</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of workplace safety standards</p></li><li><p>Diploma or degree in Construction Management, Civil Engineering, or a related field (preferred)</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary and benefits</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for career growth</p></li><li><p>Supportive and professional work environment</p></li></ul>",
